<h1>嘲</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">cháo</span><span class=alesi>(chao2)</span> , <span style="color:#990000;">zhāo</span><span class=alesi>(zhao1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 嘲 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 嘲</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/ridicule" style="color:black;">ridicule</a>, <a href="/dictionary/deride" style="color:black;">deride</a>, <a href="/dictionary/scorn" style="color:black;">scorn</a>, jeer at</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 15<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 15 strokes: <a href="/character/题" title="ti2: forehead; title, headline; theme">题</a>, <a href="/character/德" title="de2: ethics, morality, virtue">德</a>, <a href="/character/影" title="ying3: shadow; image, reflection; photograph">影</a>, <a href="/character/增" title="zeng1: increase, add to, augment">增</a>, <a href="/character/靠" title="kao4: lean on, trust, depend on; near">靠</a>, <a href="/character/额" title="e2: forehead; tablet, plaque; fixed">额</a>, <a href="/character/镇" title="zhen4: town, market place; suppress">镇</a>, <a href="/character/篇" title="pian1: chapter, section, essay, article">篇</a>, <a href="/character/暴" title="bao4: violent, brutal, tyrannical">暴</a>, <a href="/character/熟" title="shu2: well-cooked; ripe; familiar with">熟</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/口" title="Kangxi radical 30">口</a>&nbsp;30.12</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 6 <br><small>Other HSK 6 characters: <a href="/character/袍" title="pao2: long gown, robe, cloak">袍</a>, <a href="/character/衔" title="xian2: bit; hold in mouth, bite; gag">衔</a>, <a href="/character/倦" title="juan4: be tired of, weary">倦</a>, <a href="/character/涵" title="han2: soak, wet; tolerate, be lenient">涵</a>, <a href="/character/雀" title="que4: sparrow">雀</a>, <a href="/character/颁" title="ban1: confer, bestow; publish, promulgate">颁</a>, <a href="/character/舶" title="bo2: large, ocean-going vessel">舶</a>, <a href="/character/僵" title="jiang1: stiff and motionless, stock still">僵</a>, <a href="/character/辰" title="chen2: early morning; 5th terrestrial branch">辰</a>, <a href="/character/渠" title="qu2: ditch, canal, channel, gutter">渠</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-6" title="List of